 Responsive Real-World Websites

This project is part of the Udemy course by Jonas Schmedtmann,
where we learn to build responsive websites using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. 
The goal of this project is to create a fully responsive website that looks great on all devices.

Features

- Fully responsive layout that adapts to different screen sizes.
- Interactive elements using JavaScript for enhanced user experience.
- Clean and modern design with a focus on usability.
- Cross-browser compatibility.
- 
  Technologies Used

- HTML: Structure of the website.
- CSS: Styling and layout design.
- JavaScript: Interactivity and dynamic content.
-react as a framework

 
